quran[19{c,v,t}:
15,52,jab woh ibrahim ke paas aeye to salam kaha. ( unhon ne ) kaha ke hamein to tum se dar lagta hai
15,53,( mehmanon ne ) kaha ke daryay nahi hum aap ko aik danishmand larke ki khushkhabri dete hain
15,54,bolay ke jab mujhe burhapay ne aa pakra to tum khushkhabri dainay lagey. ab kaahe ki khushkhabri dete ho
15,55,( unhon ne ) kaha hum aap ko sachhi khushkhabri dete hain aap mayoos nah hoyie
15,56,( ibrahim ne ) kaha ke khuda ki rehmat se ( mein mayoos kyun honay laga is se ) mayoos hona gumrahon ka kaam hai
15,57,phir kehnay lagey ke farishto! tumhe ( aur )kiya kaam hai
15,58,( unhon ne ) kaha ke hum aik gunehgaar qoum ki taraf beje gay hain ( ke is ko azaab karen )
15,59,magar Loot ke ghar walay ke un sab ko hum bchalin ge
15,60,Albata un ki aurat ( ke ) is ke liye hum ne thehra diya hai ke woh peechay reh jaye gi
15,61,phir jab farishtay Loot ke ghar gay
15,62,to Loot ne kaha tum to na aashna se log ho
15,63,woh bolay ke nahi balkay hum aap ke paas woh cheez le kar aeye hain jis mein log shak karte they
15,64,aur hum aap ke paas yakeeni baat le kar aeye hain aur hum sach kehte hain
15,65,to aap kuch raat rahay se apne ghar walon ko le nikleen aur khud un ke peechay chalein aur aur aap mein se koi shakhs murr kar nah dekhe. aur jahan aap ko hukum ho wahan chalay jayye
15,66,aur hum ne Loot ki taraf wahi bhaije ke un logon ki jarr subah hotay hotay kaat di jaye gi
15,67,aur ahal shehar ( Loot ke paas ) khush khush ( doray ) aeye
15,68,( Loot ne ) kaha ke yeh mere mehman hain ( kahin un ke baray mein ) mujhe ruswa nah karna
15,69,aur khuda se daro. aur meri be aabrui nah ki jo
15,70,woh bolaykiya hum ne tum ko saaray Jahan ( ki himayat o tarfdari ) se mana nahikiya
